      "title": null,
      "body": "This app has a few rough edges, but generally works well. More worrying is the lack of opportunities to earn competative savings interest. The floor for me is NS&I who pay 1.16% instant access on between £500 and £1 million. Any organisation paying less than this will not get any of my money until I have filled up NS&I, which could take me a while! I can't see a need for this app (except for closing down accounts!) for most people unless savings rates improve dramatically.",
